 width apart and in line with your hips.";i:6;s:67:"Ensure you have a firm grip and lift your lower body off the chair.";i:7;s:78:"Keeping your head and chest lifted walk your feet forward until the heels are.";i:8;s:32:"Single-Chair Dips for the Chest.";i:9;s:100:"The single-chair dip is a compound exercise meaning it targets more than one muscle group at a time.";i:10;s:63:"The exercise works both of the chest muscles -- the pectoralis.";i:11;s:90:"Chair dips are the easiest variation to do and simply require a chair or bench to perform.";i:12;s:47:"Chair dips are great exercises for the triceps.";i:13;s:143:"I always thought they mainly worked the triceps but recently learned the wider scope of this exercise when I began doing them myself regularly.";i:14;s:26:"What muscles do dips work.";i:15;s:95:"The single-chair dip is a compound exercise meaning it targets more than one muscle group at a.";i:16;s:162:"Bench dips or tricep dips on bench is a compound bodyweight exercise focusing on your triceps and at the same time improving strength in your shoulders and chest.";i:17;s:105:"As the name suggests you just need a bench or chair to perform the exercise anywhere you want and can do.";i:18;s:115:"Bench or chair dips also called tricep dips are the simplest and most common dips to perform targeting the triceps.";i:19;s:126:"They work by extending and contracting the tricep muscles using the range of motion dipping below the chair or bench provides.";i:20;s:41:"A dip is an upper-body strength exercise.";i:21;s:159:"Narrow shoulder-width dips only train the triceps with major synergists being the anterior deltoid the pectoralis muscles and the rhomboid muscles of the back.";i:22;s:181:"Wide arm training places additional emphasis on the pectoral muscles similar in respect to the way a wide grip bench press would focus more on the pectorals and less on the triceps.";i:23;s:129:"If youre traveling on the road and your hotel doesnt offer a gym you can still perform exercises such as chair dips in your room.";i:24;s:109:"Exercising in your room is also a viable option if you are pressed for time or just prefer to exercise alone.";i:25;s:42:"Just imagine that you are about to sit in.";i:26;s:34:"They are a more targeted exercise.";i:27;s:100:"Triceps dips like Chest dips also target various muscles of the chest and upper region of the torso.";i:28;s:139:"However Triceps dips zero-in a little more on the Triceps than Chest dips thereby making it a better-suited exercise for that muscle group.";i:29;s:48:"To put something into a liquid for a short time.";i:30;s:37:"To put sheep for a short time into a.";i:31;s:47:"Chair dips are great exercises for the triceps.";i:32;s:107:"Learn how to work out the triceps in this free training video on upper arm exercisesSubscribe Like Share a.";i:33;s:143:"Once you have mastered performing the dips with your legs extended you can further challenge yourself by using a second chair to place them on.";i:34;s:71:"This is going to further accentuate the pressure on your chest muscles.";i:35;s:94:"Adding a second chair is certainly an advanced technique so approach with a degree of caution.";i:36;s:122:"More muscle groups activated - During dips your upper body is not supported by the bench and your feet are off the ground.";i:37;s:65:"It requires more stabilisation and activates more muscles groups.";i:38;s:74:"Wider chest development - The Dips are great in targeting the outer chest.";i:39;s:75:"This kind of exercise makes your chest look not only bigger but also wider.";i:40;s:94:"Standard dips are an advanced strength exercise that you do on a dip machine or parallel bars.";i:41;s:122:"Your body hangs above the floor and you have to press your entire body weight which is too difficult for some individuals.";i:42;s:124:"Chair dips offer the benefit of only pressing part of your body weight which makes the exercise viable for more individuals.";i:43;s:81:"Squats can mocha the difference and are great f